commands.name: az gallery service-artifact create
commands.summary: Create a Service Artifact under a gallery.
commands.syntax:
az gallery service-artifact create --gallery-name
                                   --location
                                   --name
                                   --resource-group
                                   --target-locations
                                   --vm-artifacts-profiles
                                   [--description]
                                   [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--tags]

commands.name: az gallery service-artifact get
commands.summary: Get a Service Artifact under a gallery.

commands.name: az gallery service-artifact list
commands.summary: List a list of Service Artifacts in a gallery.

commands.name: az gallery service-artifact update
commands.summary: Update a Service Artifact under a gallery.
commands.syntax:
az gallery service-artifact update [--add]
                                   [--description]
                                   [--force-string {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--gallery-name]
                                   [--ids]
                                   [--location]
                                   [--name]
                                   [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--remove]
                                   [--resource-group]
                                   [--set]
                                   [--subscription]
                                   [--tags]
                                   [--target-locations]
                                   [--vm-artifacts-profiles]

commands.name: az gallery service-artifact wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition is met.
